          "request": {
            "name": "Global System for Mobile Communications Retrieves population density information in a specified area",
            "description": {
              "content": "Retrieves population density estimation together with the estimation range related  for a time slot for a given area (described as a polygon) as a data set consisting of a sequence of equally-sized objects covering the input polygon area.",
